name: LazyDropWhileSequence.Iterator
desc: An iterator over the elements traversed by a base iterator that follow the initial consecutive elements that satisfy a given predicate.

items.name: typealias LazyDropWhileSequence.Iterator.Element
items.desc: The type of element traversed by the iterator.

items.name: func next() -> LazyDropWhileSequence<Base>.Iterator.Element?
items.desc: Advances to the next element and returns it, or nil if no next element exists.
